c: 4
v: 129
t: "Namwe ntimushobora kuba abanyakuri hagati y’abakenyezi naho mwoba mushaka kugira gutyo, rero ntimuhengamire k’uruhande rumwe kugira ngo ntimwahukane nuyo mukenyezi akaba nk’uwamanitswe, ni mwumvikana mugatinya Imana yanyu y’ukuri, Imana niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi n’impuhwe zihagije"